### Update a route mapping

```
Example Request
```

```shell
curl "https://api.example.org/v3/route_mappings/[guid]" \
  -X PATCH \
  -H "Authorization: bearer [token]" \
  -H "Content-type: application/json" \
  -d '{
    "weight": 55
  }'
```

```
Example Response
```

```http
HTTP/1.1 201 Created
Content-Type: application/json

<%= yield_content :single_route_mapping %>
```

#### Definition
`PATCH /v3/route_mappings/:guid`

#### Optional parameters

Name | Type | Description | Default
---- | ---- | ----------- | -------
**weight**  | int         | A relative weight for your application that must be between 1 and 128.

